Package: fertplanspatial
Type: Package
Title: Compute And Spatialize NPK Fertilization Plans
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2020-04-29
Authors@R: c(person("Marco", "Bascietto", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                     email = "marco.bascietto@crea.gov.it"))
Description: From physical and chemical analyses of soil samples to spatialized 
    fertilization plans for field crops: build spatial maps of nutrient 
    deficiencies to support farmers and professionals in precise distribution 
    of N,P,K-based fertilizers.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/mbask/fertplanspatial
BugReports: https://github.com/mbask/fertplanspatial/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    fertplan,
    data.table,
    ensurer,
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    sp,
    gstat,
    automap
Suggests: 
    tinytest,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    ggplot2,
    raster
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
VignetteBuilder: knitr
